                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">'hitting the nail on the head'
<br />

<br />
A warrior friend of mine actually helped me come to what I think is a concise summary of the problem.
<br />

<br />
Problem 1. Verant nerfs the enchanter class severely in Velious but gives us upgraded charm (via the mobs we can utilize) in Luclin to compensate.
<br />
Problem 2. SOE nerfs the enchanter class severely in OoW to do away with the charm leaving us with about as much *relative* power as we had in the Velious era without the charms.
<br />

<br />
We have been severely nerfed for different reasons by two separate companies with no communication with one another. As of yet there has been no compensation for the second severe nerf.
<br />

<br />
/shrug that's just how I see it.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 10px; line-height: normal"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=361216" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ariu <span style="font-style: italic">stop destroying my class damnit!</span> Vil''''Aki &lt;Heroes&gt;</a>
