What other class regresses as they gain(?) new levels?
<br />
49 abilities : charm, fear kite, ae stun, ae mez, mez's that last long enough to hold 7 - 10 mobs, minor buffs
<br />
Group desirability: Must have.
<br />

<br />
56 abilities : charm, mez, minor buffs, ae mez with  the duration of a stun, ae stun
<br />
Group desirability: An asset.
<br />

<br />
65 abilities : charm, mez, ae mez with a duration of a stun, ae stun, ae mez that can only be gotten from a locked zone.
<br />
Group desirability: Must we?
<br />

<br />
70 abilities : minor buffs (unable to mez due to high MR or level cap and charm unjustifiable)
<br />
Group desirability: None
<br />

<br />
By group desirability I mean to get asked to join a pick up group, not friends. Friends ask you to group no matter what class or abilities you have.....they're your friends.
<br />

<br />
That's not even getting into the degredation of faction in which we were supposed to excel in.
<br />

<br />
You're response may be different than what I'm hearing....but what I'm hearing is...working as intended, have a nice day.
<br />

<br />
I find the dismissiveness, indifference and disrespect of time investment an insult.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
